John K. SUCKOW, Appellant, v. BORAX CONSOLIDATED, Inc., Appellee. No. 7506. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 8, 1934. Wm. H. Neblett, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Newlin & Ashbum, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel, ordered appeal dismissed, mandate forthwith.
